    Function that compuate the maximum uptakes for all sequences in the dataset

    maxUptakes.Rd

    Function that compuate the maximum uptakes for all sequences in the dataset

    maxUptakes(res)

    Arguments

    res

    An object of class DataFrame containing the results of the hdx-ms experiment

    Value

    Returns a numeric vector of maximum uptakes

    Examples

    
data("BRD4_apo")
BRD4_apo <- DataFrame(BRD4_apo)

maxUptakes(res = BRD4_apo)
